To tar a folder verbosely
	tar cvf folder.tar folder/

To use gzip  z
	tar cvfz folder.tar.gz folder/

To use bzip2 ( smaller but slower)
	tar cvfj folder.tar.bz2 folder/

To extract
	tar xvfz / tar xvfj

